There's a check,

40:49.295 --> 40:52.196
But it's not from the whale.

40:56.134 --> 40:57.934
Dad paid us back.

40:57.935 --> 41:01.304
Every Penny.

41:01.305 --> 41:03.739
How does it feel to be
so consistently wrong?

41:03.740 --> 41:05.007
In this case,

41:05.008 --> 41:08.243
I'm not so sure how it feels.

41:08.244 --> 41:09.844
As much as I'd like
to tape Eddie's check

41:09.845 --> 41:11.211
Over our cash register,

41:11.212 --> 41:12.679
I guess you should deposit it,

41:12.680 --> 41:14.647
After our thank you lunch
with newberg.

