like, an infinity pool

41:25.758 --> 41:27.125
Or a helicopter or, like, a...

41:27.126 --> 41:28.359
No, a g-5.
We're getting a g-5.

41:28.360 --> 41:29.860
That's what it is.

41:29.861 --> 41:31.662
So you take the girl,
I'll take the jet.

41:31.663 --> 41:33.533
- I don't want the girl.
- I'll take them both then.

41:33.534 --> 41:36.069
Hank? Perfect timing.

41:36.070 --> 41:38.272
Lunch is just being put out.

41:38.273 --> 41:39.607
Allow me.

