and finish cooking school.

41:44.780 --> 41:46.947
She sounds so happy.

41:46.948 --> 41:48.782
There's no greater joy

41:48.783 --> 41:50.384
Than seeing your child happy.

41:50.385 --> 41:51.985
Every parent deserves that.

41:51.986 --> 41:55.288
And, Hank, I've gotta
say thank you.

41:55.289 --> 41:56.857
Your advice
was very meaningful.

41:56.858 --> 41:57.858
My advice?

